{
  "name": "Beast Imitating Art Lizard",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Non%20Elemental.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You summon an inky lizard in a space you can see within range that can hold it. The lizard is a construct with the following statistics;</p><p>• AC 12, 5d6 (20) Hit points.</p><p>The lizard immediately after being summoned, screeches a menacing sound to those around it. All creatures who begin their turn within 10 feet of the lizard excluding you, must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save they gain 1 rank of Fear. So long as a<br />creature has ranks of fear gained as a result of this jutsu they cannot willingly approach the Lizard.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the range of the lizards Screech by 5 feet.</p>",
